Note: 
- Road speed limits and game conditions may still apply.
- Also install **Road Speed Adjuster** mod to double road speeds and see better Bike results.
- Safe to remove any time. For fastest "reset to game defaults" save the city, then remove. 
- If you uncheck the enable box, it disables the mod if you don't want to uninstall it.

